data.description: FANTASTIC HOME THAT HAS BEEN WELL CARED FOR AND HAS TONS OF SPACE! HUGE Eat In Kitchen with Quartz Counter tops, Stainless Steel appliances, and Hardwood Floors. Spacious Living Room, Formal Dining Room, Master Suite with Private entrance, Accessible Ramp and Doorways. Main Floor also has Two more Bedrooms, a Full Bath, Laundry Room and a Large Covered Deck that overlooks the Beautiful Treed lot. If you are needing EXTRA space there is a Full Apartment on the Lower Level with a Bonus Room, Laundry, Full Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances, Living Room, Full Bath, Two Non-Conforming Bedrooms, and a Private Entrance and Driveway! Close to Schools, Restaurants, Shopping, and Highway access. This Home Has so Many Possibilities!  COME SEE FOR YOURSELF!
